headline.print_headline: No Bail for Oregon College Athlete in Man's Death
headline.main: No Bail for Oregon College Athlete in Man's Death

lead_paragraph: An Oregon college football player charged with killing a 66-year-old man was being held without bail Friday following a court appearance that shed no light on the circumstances of the alleged crime, which has shocked and baffled many in the student's school and hometown.
